category of genuinely puzzling maritime salvage—require multi-school analytical frameworks. The
Shrine's assessment protocol formally includes Confluence Text cross-reference when Axiomatic
single-school analysis is inconclusive. The Swift Court accepts Shrine assessments using Confluence
Text methodology as expert testimony without requiring additional Axiomatic credentialing, which
is occasionally contested by Midgaard's academic partners in joint provenance proceedings.

